This is a 'list of lists of the municipalities of [[Spain]]'. The municipalities
list links are listed below, by autonomous community and province.

According to the provisional reports released on 1 January 2012, [http://www.ine.es/jaxi/menu.do?type=pcaxis&path=%2Ft20%2Fe260%2Fa2009%2F&file-
=pcaxis&N=&L=0 INE] (provisional report). 1 January 2012. there is a total
of 8,116 municipalities in Spain, including the autonomous cities of Ceuta and
Melilla. Burgos is the province with the most municipalities (371) and Las
Palmas the one with the least (34).
